      "content": "A typical Sunday dinner scene in a Black family household would be a chaotic, loud, and loving mess. The aroma of fried chicken, collard greens, and mac and cheese would fill the air, making your stomach growl with hunger. The sound of laughter, arguing, and gospel music would create a lively atmosphere, with everyone gathered around the table, passing plates and sharing stories. The TV would be blaring in the background, with a sports game or a family favorite show playing, adding to the energy. It would be a scene of warmth, tradition, and community, with everyone coming together to celebrate the end of the week.",
